title: Just a pug riding a mechanical horse to the Bonanza theme music
text:
Doug the pug , to be precise.
You know, the pug that has over 2.6 million likes on Facebook , 844k followers on Instagram and rakes up YouTube views like they're going out of fashion and is now a commissioned actor .
Sometimes we forget how much of a ridiculous place the internet is. Thankfully we have Doug here to remind us.
Via YouTube
